%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9e7c527a6f66a8c49a6fab10a94681fc, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day2NightN
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  sequenceId: albert_day2_morning_nopill
  lines:
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Hey there, Andy. The logs show that wiring in the navigation room is operational.
      How was the fix-up?
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Just the standard procedure. Re-routed the pathways and avoided
        crossing paths. Everything\u2019s in the clear. Hopefully, things stay like
        that for a while."
      nextLineIndex: 1
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: It was fine.
      nextLineIndex: 2
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "You always followed protocol the best out of all the people I\u2019ve
      known. Keep that up, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll be well taken care of by
      DOLOS."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Straight to the point. Can\u2019t argue with the results."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "On a different note, you didn\u2019t seem like yourself this morning.
      I can\u2019t quite put my finger on why. Is everything alright on your end?
      Got any questions you need answered?"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices:
    - choiceText: "I\u2019m just reviewing and keeping myself reminded about the
        contract. Staying sharp is all. There\u2019s nothing wrong with that, right?"
      nextLineIndex: 4
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "I\u2019ve been thinking about how precise and meticulous everything
        has to be. The doses in the collar, the data logs\u2026 all that stuff that
        DOLOS collects from us."
      nextLineIndex: 6
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "I had a weird dream a while ago that I thought about recently.
        About Earth, actually. Just got me thinking about some stuff\u2026"
      nextLineIndex: 10
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "I found something peculiar in the system yesterday. An old technician\u2019s
        log. Part of one, anyway. The name was Fiske. Mean anything to you?"
      nextLineIndex: 14
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: That's about all I wanted to ask.
      nextLineIndex: 20
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 1
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 1
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Of course. Nothing wrong with that at all.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 5
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "It\u2019s always smart to know the rulebook that you live under. Compliance
      is stability, and stability is safety."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "That\u2019s how DOLOS wants things up here. Precision is what keeps a
      tin can like the SUNSET16 functional in the void of space. One of our competitors
      from a few years ago didn\u2019t follow that line of reasoning."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: What happened to them anyway?
      nextLineIndex: 7
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "It\u2019s a good thing that I applied here then."
      nextLineIndex: 9
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "The answer that\u2019s known to the public was that the shareholders got
      too greedy, and the company collapsed from the inside."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: And the real answer?
      nextLineIndex: 8
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Remains classified to high-ranking DOLOS personnel only.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: You and me both. The DOLOS Corporation is a very stable company. All thanks
      to Erebus Holdings.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Dreams can be like that. But that\u2019s why the capsule pills help with
      that. They stabilize your sleeping patterns, among all the other benefits they
      provide us on board the SUNSET16."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: Right. The pills.
      nextLineIndex: 11
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "\u2026You did take your dosage today, right, Andy?"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "I\u2019ve been here for 5 years already, and I\u2019ve adhered
        to company policy this whole time. I have no reason to break it now."
      nextLineIndex: 12
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: Of course. Would the logs say otherwise?
      nextLineIndex: 13
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Good. Just checking\u2026 for your own wellbeing."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: The logs only show dispensation requests. I trust you to follow protocol,
      as per your contract.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "\u2026That\u2019s a name I haven\u2019t seen in a while. Where\u2019d
      you find that?"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "In an unsuspecting terminal. I can\u2019t recall which one."
      nextLineIndex: 15
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "\u2026Pay no attention to them. Files like that are old and are sometimes
      corrupted with malware. You\u2019ll get your computer infected if you keep
      interacting with it."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 16
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: DOLOS issued an announcement a while ago on matters like this. You should
      brush up on it.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Alright\u2026 I won\u2019t pry further."
      nextLineIndex: 17
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    - choiceText: "Then\u2026 who was Fiske?"
      nextLineIndex: 18
      offPillChoice: 1
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: albert_corrupted_logs
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Good.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "\u2026Someone who didn\u2019t follow protocol. He was put on administrative
      leave for an undisclosed amount of time."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 19
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "We shouldn\u2019t talk about him anymore. Listen to DOLOS and adhere to
      your contract, as you have been doing these past 5 years."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Anyways, my late-night shift is about to start. Don\u2019t stay up too
      late. Tomorrow is another beautiful day of productivity."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: Night, Al.
      nextLineIndex: 21
      offPillChoice: 0
      showOnRepeat: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: 
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: -1
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
    loreEntry: 
